1. Create some qr codes of names of person whose attendance is going to be monitored
2. run generatingQR.py python file and enter number of people you want to add
3. Add there names
4. Now QR Codes folder would be populated with the qr codes you just created
5. Goto the scanningQR.py file and run it
6. put your generated qr code in front of camera and scan them
7. Press e when done to close the camera
8. open your mysql cli and fire queries in TABLE DEFINITION in MYSQL.txt
9. Run updateDBMS.py file
10. It will automatically update the data on the attendance.txt file to the mysql server